<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش ل ح<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٧٧ - ش ل ح]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شلَّحَ يشلِّح، تشليحًا، فهو مُشلِّح، والمفعول مُشلَّح<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شلَّح الشَّخصَ:</span> عَرّى بعضَ جسدِه، جرَّده من ثيابه جزئيًّا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>